Entries.default: "Why do the vithrack keep this if they don't use it?"
"A curious collection. Do the vithrack here think it trash or treasure, I wonder?"
"Take what you need. I doubt the vithrack have use for it."
"Spider booty, aye? Don't mind if I do."
"Well, it ain't like they're using it."
"A monument to agony and loss. We should leave these goods where they fell."
"Are they stealin' this stuff off those folks in the Collections, or is this all comin' from topside?"
"I wonder at the tensile strength of this webbing."
"These are no good to the dead."
